1
00:00:00,649 --> 00:00:01,614
LISA: Aah!
MARGE: Whoo!

2
00:00:01,650 --> 00:00:02,615
BART:
Wha...!

3
00:00:02,651 --> 00:00:03,616
(Homer grunts)

4
00:00:03,652 --> 00:00:04,652
D'oh!

5
00:00:07,055 --> 00:00:08,221
D'oh!

6
00:00:08,256 --> 00:00:09,256
(tires screeching)

7
00:00:10,959 --> 00:00:12,425
♪ I don't believe it ♪

8
00:00:12,460 --> 00:00:13,927
♪ When you tell me ♪

9
00:00:13,962 --> 00:00:15,428
♪ That it's all gone bad ♪

10
00:00:15,463 --> 00:00:16,930
♪ It's true ♪

11
00:00:16,965 --> 00:00:18,264
♪ To... you... ♪

12
00:00:18,300 --> 00:00:19,265
Whoa!

13
00:00:19,301 --> 00:00:20,300
(tires screech)

14
00:00:20,324 --> 00:00:24,324
<font color="#00FF00">♪ The Simpsons 27x01 ♪</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">Every Man's Dream</font>
